    <h1>Lassi Karjalainen</h1>
    <h3>Bachelor of Technology in Information and Software Technology, Master's student in Technology Management</h3>
    <h3>Corporate Relations Coordinator at the Student Union of the University of Jyväskylä, Linkki NakkiJYYstäjä, Linkki opposition and Poliukko</h3>
    <p>Email: lassikarjalainen0@gmail.com</p>
