    <p>General nick: LKKarjalainen</p>

    <h2>Who</h2>
    <p>I am a 23-year-old Master's student in Technology Management at the University of Jyväskylä. I enjoy many hobbies like MTG, computer hardware and light videogame pirating.</p>
    <p>I have work experience mainly in test automation and manual testing. I have also served as a patent specialist and business consultant. In my studies I have focused on computational programming and business studies.</p>

    <h2>What</h2>
    <p>Projects: <a href="https://github.com/LKKarjalainen">GitHub</a></p>
    <p>Profile: <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/lassikarjalainen/">LinkedIn</a></p>
