    <p>I participate in the events of Linkki, Ynnä, Algo and JYY in varying amounts. The best event ever is definitely Jyväsmetro.</p>
    <p>I am also known in places like <a href="https://linkkijkl.fi/kattila/">Kattila</a>, Teerenpeli and <a href="https://jyväskylä.hacklab.fi/">Hacklab Jyväskylä</a>.</p>

    <h2>Where</h2>
    <p>Jyväskylä, or casually Jykylä.</p>
    <p>I am often found in Kattila. Kattila's <a href="https://kattila.linkkijkl.fi/">visitor tracker</a> can show if "LKKarjalainen" is there.</p>
    <p>The fastest way to reach me electronically is by calling or on Telegram.</p>

